        "Title": "Financial Sabotage",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ROCKY_DUGONG",
        "PublicId": "134769878406",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Rocky/scene_dugong.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 5bab73bb-1f5d-4bde-b6d5-48cc7c3a6c62).Image",
        "Description": "Good day.\r\rRecently, I have in real life been looking at flights and hotels for a trip to Virginia and Florida. I am quite excited about this excursion, but not very much at the prices. Right now they are generally very high, but come to find out, there is another explanation for this.\r\rThe pirates on Ambrose Island apparently have a cybercrime division, and they have hacked many booking websites to display higher prices which is then sent to the hackers. This needs to be stopped.\r\rBest of luck.",
